Background\par
Tomoe was born to the Kakita family and raised in the courts of the Crane\par
clan. Her iaijutsu form is quick and precise, though her tendency to\par
contradict her peers has made her a difficult presence at formal events.\par
Despite this, her charm and kind eyes have earned her the respect of her\par
sensei.\par
\par
Appearance\par
Tall for a Crane, with pale silver hair kept in a long braid. Wears the\par
muted colors of the Kakita Dueling Academy and carries a katana forged by\par
her grandmother.\par

